            . I am a <rs id="t18180114-171-viclabel925" type="occupation">labourer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-171-victim1180 t18180114-171-viclabel925"></join>, and live in Black Lion-yard, Golden-lane. The prisoner nursed my wife-on the 13th of September she left, and we missed the articles stated in the indictment. On the 23d of December I found her at St. Sepulchre's workhouse, and charged her with the robbery. She said the devil persuaded her to commit it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180114-171-person1182">
                  MARY 
                  HUGHES
               <interp inst="t18180114-171-person1182" type="surname" value="HUGHES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180114-171-person1182" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180114-171-person1182" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the prosecutor's wife. The prisoner left in the middle of the night of the 12th of September - I thought she was gone to bed; she never returned. We missed the articles stated in the indictment; I found my gown on her back when she was taken.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I beg for mercy.</p>
